msgid "Vortem.ai Setup Wizard"
msgstr "Vortem.ai sozlash ustasi"

msgid "Thank you for choosing vortem.ai Plugin. This wizard will help you set up your store quickly and easily."
msgstr "vortem.ai plaginini tanlaganingiz uchun tashakkur. Ushbu usta doʻkoningizni tez va oson sozlashga yordam beradi."

msgid "To use Vortem's product selling services, you need an AliExpress account. You can connect your account from Settings → Vortem Login → AliExpress Integration. If you don't have an account, you can sign up directly from there."
msgstr "Vortem mahsulotlarini sotish xizmatlaridan foydalanish uchun sizga AliExpress hisobi kerak. Hisobingizni Sozlamalar → Vortem kirish → AliExpress integratsiyasi orqali ulashingiz mumkin. Agar sizda hisob bo'lmasa, u yerdan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri ro'yxatdan o'tishingiz mumkin."

msgid "To use Vortem's product selling services, you need an AliExpress account."
msgstr "Vortem mahsulotlarini sotish xizmatlaridan foydalanish uchun sizga AliExpress hisobi kerak."

msgid "You can connect your account from Settings → Vortem Login → AliExpress Integration."
msgstr "Hisobingizni Sozlamalar → Vortem kirish → AliExpress integratsiyasi orqali ulashingiz mumkin."

msgid "If you don't have an account, you can sign up directly from there."
msgstr "Agar sizda hisob bo'lmasa, u yerdan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri ro'yxatdan o'tishingiz mumkin."

