msgid "Terms & Conditions"
msgstr "Foydalanish shartlari"

msgid "1. License Agreement"
msgstr "1. Litsenziya shartnomasi"

msgid "By using this plugin, you agree to comply with all applicable laws and regulations. The plugin is provided under the GPL v2 or later license."
msgstr "Ushbu plagindan foydalanish orqali siz barcha amaldagi qonun va qoidalarga rioya qilishga rozilik bildirasiz. Plagin GPL v2 yoki undan keyingi litsenziya asosida taqdim etiladi."

